= Experimentell =
== Sechseck Lampe ==
 * Topic: actors/misc/honeycomb0
 * Funktionen
  * mode [0..46]
  * speed [0..255]
  * brightness [0..255]
  * color [#rrgbb] Hex Werte
 * Nette modes:
  * FX_MODE_FIREWORKS, mode 42, speed 255
  * FX_MODE_STROBE_RAINBOW, mode 24, speed 190
  * FX_MODE_HYPER_SPARKLE, mode  22, speed 0
  * FX_MODE_FADE, mode  12, speed 20
  * FX_MODE_RAINBOW_CYCLE, mode  9, speed 0
  * FX_MODE_STATIC 0

